

                          [help castle]
-----------------------=========+=========-----------------------



Usage: castle <wizardname>
Cost: 5 spell points
Level: 10

This spell will take you directly to the outside
of a particular wizard's castle entrance.

For example: 'castle vertebraker' will bring you to Vertebraker's
castle entrance.

You cannot teleport out of an area that you are in,
you must be in the village or the outlying forests/plains.

